1. *Sigurni* smo da će sve biti u redu. (We are sure that everything will be alright.)
2. Oni su *sigurni* da nema nikakvih problema. (They are sure that there are no problems.) 
3. Njegove odluke su izuzetno *sigurne*. (His decisions are extremely secure.)
4. Oni su *sigurni* da će napraviti uspešan posao. (They are sure that they will do a successful job.)
5. *Sigurno* je da ćemo dobiti odgovore. (It is certain that we will get answers.)